Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1184,954)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,904)}美食
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(904,480)}超值装\N美食
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, who is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.90,0:01:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在盛装打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just getting dressed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要出游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna hang out?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't right now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可是小蜗的重要日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a big day for Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的蜗牛成年礼已经到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His snail-mitzvah already?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天他得去  看兽医
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today he's going to the V-E-T
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然想和你去  但我没穿兽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd join you, but I'm not dressed for the zoo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是看病的那个兽医
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The vet, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.71,0:02:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗讨厌去兽医院体检
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary hates going to the vet for his checkup
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我每次都得骗小蜗进宠物提篮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I always have to trick him into the pet carrier
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.83,0:02:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地留了一道蜗牛粮  放在卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left a trail of SnailPo treats around the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,引下楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down the stairs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿过客厅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through the living room
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进了厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and into the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.57,0:02:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗就会在那发现一堆点心  就在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where he'll find a pile of treats right inside
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物提篮里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his pet carrier
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还在吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still there, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.97,0:02:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好办法  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great plan, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗一定会上当的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's gonna fall for it for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.02,0:03:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me just
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定比我想的还要难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be harder than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一点蜗牛粮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More snail food, please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,526)}蜗牛笑话
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来单纯散个步了  绝对没另有所图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,time for an innocent walk with no ulterior motive
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你得去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you need to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see your doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.92,0:03:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能得来个更诡谲的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll need a ruse that's even rusier
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管那个笨兽医了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget that silly veterinarian
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给咱俩预定了豪华热带假期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I booked a big tropical vacation just for the two of us
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出游放松一阵子是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't it be nice to just get away for a while and relax?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.25,0:04:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进度假提篮里  我们就能起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So just get into that vacation carriage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we can take off
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  快点进宠物提篮里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary, just get in that pet carrier
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1158,424)}裤头村机场
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be a good snail
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两周后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我重返青春了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel rejuvenated
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这封信是寄给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This letter came for you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是封邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an invitation
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邀请你去败蜗子家开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a big party at Snail Fail's house
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可是这附近最出名的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is the most famous snail in town
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:05:00.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,826)}邀请函\N盛大派对\N\N就在败蜗子家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:05:00.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,842)}贵宾
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是他的贵宾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're his VIP
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他连豪车都派出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He even sent a limousine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先请  我的大好蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After you, my good snail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:26.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,164)}蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很奢华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty fancy, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜兽医预约看诊只好取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pity we'll have to cancel that vet appointment
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可绝对不能错过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but there's no way we could miss
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我可不容错过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pretty hard to miss
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.22,0:05:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:02.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1420,554)}命中情蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到  命中情蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to Snails of Our Lives
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是小蜗不信我说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't convince Gary by lying to him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就非让他信我的逆耳真言不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to convince him with brutal honesty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上实行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道德绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the guilt trip
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一期  命中情蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time on Snails of Our Lives
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I'm begging you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你去看兽医吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please go to the veterinarian
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都担心死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm worried sick about you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会是想让我死吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to be sick, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.27,0:06:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会还要早早送我入土吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to send me to an early grave?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意为你做任何事  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would do anything for you, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最佳表演奖得主是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the winner for best acting is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能得到提名真是莫大的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was an honor just to be nominated
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你早十一分钟前告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you had told me eleven minutes ago
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝无论如何都会获奖  我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that little old SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would win an award for anything, I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见见又鬼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又让那只滑头蜗牛逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sneaky snail got away again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要带小蜗看兽医
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am taking Gary to the vet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by any means necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a1\pos(1220,716)}倘若立下决心\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N打碎玻璃
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不当好好海绵先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Mr. Nice Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猎捕蜗牛时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for a snail hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是温的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still warm
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚死的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fresh kill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,804)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.13,0:08:07.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:07.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你正好落入了我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you've fallen into one of the many traps
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在家里设了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've set around the house
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给点隐私啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little privacy please?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兽医时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vet time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着红点走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,follow the dot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是理性思考一下吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just think rationally here, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,448)}兽医
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以把你家蜗牛带进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may bring in your snail now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的牙齿可真健康
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What healthy teeth you have
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  对好心的医生温柔点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, be nice to the kind doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's quite alright, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.01,0:10:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要怎么对付凶狠的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how to handle vicious snails
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棒棒糖就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lollipop
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All done
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.89,0:10:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是个医用棒棒糖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a medical lollipop
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面富含各种维生素和疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,full of all the vitamins and vaccinations
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是蜗牛成长必备的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a growing snail needs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来也不是很糟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't so bad after all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明年见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya next year
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不能走  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't leave, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你全身都是咬痕和抓痕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're covered in bites and scratches
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.17,0:11:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗在来的路上确实有点粗暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary did get a little rough on the way over here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该也有棒棒糖吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take a lollipop, too
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.85,0:11:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  海绵可没有棒棒糖吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, sponges don't get lollipops
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不能遭到感染  所以你得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get infected, so you'll need
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接受全套治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the full treatment
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想去看兽医啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go to the vet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.02,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}千斤压顶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(716,406)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(734,698)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:55.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(578,476)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,692)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And five
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And four
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And three
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great job
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的热身完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've finished your warm-up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.07,0:12:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再投两毛五  进入真正的健身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now pop in another quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let's get to the real workout
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.05,0:12:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天热个身就行  鹈鹕机器先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just the warm-up today, Mr. Pelican machine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来的健身活动是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for my next workout
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打拳击吊袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The speed bag
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:44.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(694,272)}我爱痛苦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受身体燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel the burn
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天  我要推向极限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today, I am pushing it to the limit
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来破自己记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for a new personal best
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Half
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.34,0:13:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pinned
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你能想出解决办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob, you can figure this out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.56,0:13:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep calm
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用脚指头走路就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll let my foot fingers do the walking
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里肯定有东西能帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something in here that can help me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  太多齿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, too toothy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太辣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too spicy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太撬棍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too crowbar-y
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太躁动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too snappy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗可以救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary will save me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in here, buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,478)}喵喵喵喵\N喵喵喵喵\N喵喵喵喵
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Garebear
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被压在这杠铃底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped beneath this bar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托帮我弄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come get it off me, please
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这样就对了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little closer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小家伙都累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor little guy's all tuckered out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过不太确定这有没有帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not sure this is helping me though
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗向来都会往自己壳里放签字笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary always keeps a journaling pen inside his shell
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eureka
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Send help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困在楼上健身房的杠铃下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've become trapped under my weights in my upstairs gym
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家蜗牛的名字叫小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My snail's name is Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗也在  不过睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary is here too, but he fell asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我只能靠你了  好心的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm relying on you, kind stranger"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.52,0:15:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得救马上就只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon it'll be just a matter of time before I'm rescued
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:29.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,728)}海草哥
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意谁扔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, who threw this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了  大聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That does it, wisenheimer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom Police Department
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么公安服务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How may I protect and serve?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An assault
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村绝不能出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not in our town
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上派出警船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll send a squad boat right away
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.07,0:16:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往警船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the cop mobile
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吧  神秘恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that, mysterious miscreant?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are so
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I'm saved
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说地址在哪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that address again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:41.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,568)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.17,0:16:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  那家伙老是乱报警
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, that guy's always calling
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  上次他报警是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, last time it was because of
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自家客厅闯进了一只海苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a trespassing sea-fly in his living room
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死  他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, shrimp, there he is
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弯下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duck
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这  警官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here, officers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.40,0:17:02.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:02.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.05,0:17:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码警察那边确实有说要派出警船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they did say they were gonna send a squad boat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴一群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警察没停船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They didn't stop
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把瓶子撞出窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must knock bottle out of window
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些健身器材终于能派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally I can put these gym tools to use
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没东西可扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing left to throw
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're my only hope
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把瓶子砸出窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,try to knock the bottle out of the window
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下彻底玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've really done it now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有希望都破灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hope is lost
