Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've tried everything and failed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.10,0:17:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有想得到的逃生机会  都用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All conceivable chances of escape, exhausted
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the phone
