Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pinned under weights in my home gym
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's correct
