Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来十分钟内抵达电台即可领取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you can get down here to the station
