Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't hang up
