Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure to call somebody
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困在我杠铃底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped under my weights
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然很希望能帮到你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help you, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.32,0:18:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里自己都有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry's got problems of his own
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说被困住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trapped, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就自己一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All alone?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还动弹不得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can't move?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.72,0:19:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真难受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,excruciating
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  打错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, wrong number
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很多小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,H-help
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在谁都不会来救你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no one who can help you now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友会找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my friends will find me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们连你在哪都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't even know where you are
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.19,0:19:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们知道你在哪  大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we know where you are, big silly
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们直到你生命尽头都会是你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be your friends to the end of your days
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm saved
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in
