Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you home?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't hear anything
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The coast is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是海绵宝宝这辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the best surprise party
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最厉害的惊喜派对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon I'll be free
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.28,0:20:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:20:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,楼上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,upstairs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道楼上有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of fun stuff is up there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are ye doing, lads?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.57,0:21:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只准在楼下指定的派对区嬉笑打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your mirth and mayhem downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the designated party area
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们听不见我的求救声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They can't hear my voice
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但可能可以听得见我的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But maybe they can hear my foot's voice
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.34,0:21:46.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:46.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.91,0:21:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得这首船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this shanty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.32,0:21:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在我家健身房被杠铃压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pinned under weights in my home gym
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天  我本想锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By Jove, by Jim I tried to be trim
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却在我家健身房被杠铃压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pinned under weights in my home gym
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我试图变壮  但远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to get buff but it wasn't enough
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重压之下  举步维艰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When the weight had its way, the going got tough
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能摇不能垫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No shimmy or shim
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的颤抖四肢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My quivering limbs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我家健身房被杠铃压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinned under weights in my home gym
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快将杠铃举过身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, hoist the barbells over lads
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尚未入水就会沉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll sink before they swim
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.42,0:22:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就多花点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I should have paid extra
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修个防船歌地板了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the shanty-proof floor
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,358)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.18,0:22:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我今早才差点上班迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's why I was almost late for work this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间了  快干活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop your lollygagging and get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.82,0:22:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
